race.description: Independent Liquor Group Ipswich Derby Final (G3)
race.comment: VALIDATE (2) comes off a (25.07) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a OPEN over 457m at this track. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks well placed and should feature. GREVILLEA (5) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and three minors from seven tries. Recorded a 10 length win (24.86) in a OPEN last time at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. UNRULY BOY (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with three wins and a placing from six tries. Recorded a 1.75 lengths win (25.34) in a OPEN last time at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. FIRE ME UP (3) is always a threat when he draws this box.
